<normalizedToken id="3C5A7C332D88B23996223751BFDCDCE4" originalValue="alpícola" pageId="null" pageNumber="394">alpicola</normalizedToken>
De la Soie
</taxonomicName>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="D4E93B7D79CF0FC9B1EF284EAF3796B2" pageId="null" pageNumber="394" type="vernacular_names">
<paragraph id="643D96630308E873434F125B44736DEA" pageId="null" pageNumber="394">Alpen-Fingerkraut</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="37B1B2A998B64A53E74434ABED9ABF50" pageId="null" pageNumber="394" type="description">
<paragraph id="BE9ACFB738D53754E50EF049C067AB98" pageId="null" pageNumber="394">
<taxonomicName id="610404EE74D11B72BCBE878440B8C1FC" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Rosaceae" genus="Potentilla" kingdom="Plantae" order="Rosales" pageId="null" pageNumber="394" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="alpicola">
<emphasis id="1527B2D067A7090BD2617C0E806B4D68" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="394">P. alpicola</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
unterscheidet sich von 
<taxonomicName id="414BB462FBE70C5DB426CD6C48EB369A" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Rosaceae" genus="Potentilla" kingdom="Plantae" order="Rosales" pageId="null" pageNumber="394" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="leucopolitana">
<emphasis id="C2F4E86E9D941BC53904475FF00DA5BF" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="394">P. leucopolitana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 13c) durch die Behaarung der Blattunterseite: 
<emphasis id="67893C7D391CA64F1CA0865A531B8E57" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="394">
Filzige Behaarung sehr locker, so 
<normalizedToken id="BDE0FDB495DA86A0CC87563D34261890" originalValue="daß" pageId="null" pageNumber="394">dass</normalizedToken>
Blattunterseite 
<normalizedToken id="EB5CD5F0AFE92C60D20195DDDEF56B40" originalValue="grün" pageId="null" pageNumber="394">gruen</normalizedToken>
, zahlreiche gerade Haare
</emphasis>
nicht nur 
<pageBreakToken id="1A7885CCB239229EA30ED8188C2AB23A" pageId="null" pageNumber="394">auf</pageBreakToken>
den Nerven (wie bei den vorhergehenden Arten der Gruppe) sondern 
<emphasis id="2C001E639720B5DAAC4A917872835CAA" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="394">
<normalizedToken id="8F4F37FE42E760A814D3BFA4D73F77AC" originalValue="über" pageId="null" pageNumber="394">ueber</normalizedToken>
die ganze Blatt-Unterseite verteilt.
</emphasis>
- 
<normalizedToken id="8940650F2105D21E14679E27B810B955" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="394">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: 
<normalizedToken id="BCCAEB15EA0CD586B3572A48DA2F48CE" originalValue="Frühling" pageId="null" pageNumber="394">Fruehling</normalizedToken>
und 
<normalizedToken id="7B599D493D7A1EFC7310EDFC23659057" originalValue="Frühsommer" pageId="null" pageNumber="394">Fruehsommer</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="3E618F4027E304EAAD41C832232F6E2F" pageId="null" pageNumber="394">
<emphasis id="AED337E083457AA16EEF2EEF9B54E9CF" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="394">Zytologische Angaben.</emphasis>
Keine Untersuchungen.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="CA4E87425C5E347233FCB615A8772AF3" pageId="null" pageNumber="394">
<emphasis id="095164702D63B9FD2EEE7BC1E49FD051" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="394">Standort.</emphasis>
Kollin, seltener montan. Keine 
<normalizedToken id="E4B90214CB6C4FB3B7FE79867EACEC09" originalValue="näheren" pageId="null" pageNumber="394">naeheren</normalizedToken>
Angaben, wahrscheinlich wie bei 
<taxonomicName id="BC527B8A59730CAD15BDA015CB2EDC21" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Rosaceae" genus="Potentilla" kingdom="Plantae" order="Rosales" pageId="null" pageNumber="394" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="leucopolitana">
<emphasis id="EB5035E270C7265010CE10FD4425EDA4" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="394">P. leucopolitana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 13c).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="CAE492CCF4347775AB90C09D4696392C" pageId="null" pageNumber="394">
<emphasis id="7E579D77B0618D04E5B348791DFD6FF7" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="394">Verbreitung. Mittelalpen-Pflanze:</emphasis>
Durch Walliser Alpen und Piemont 
<normalizedToken id="A74E7BD901140E2EAB0AB87716FF60C7" originalValue="ostwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="394">ostwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis 
<normalizedToken id="8C2C98FD305C2AC1EC20C3CF63FCD434" originalValue="Südtirol" pageId="null" pageNumber="394">Suedtirol</normalizedToken>
. - Aus dem Gebiet wenig gesicherte Angaben: Wallis, Centovalli, Sarnico bei Bergamo, Unterengadin, 
<normalizedToken id="CDB0AF2D29DAD6426660BCA6974E0030" originalValue="Münstertal" pageId="null" pageNumber="394">Muenstertal</normalizedToken>
, Vintschgau.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
